post_text:
Dear Parents/Guardians;

Back to school night is this Wednesday, August 22nd from 6-7:30 pm. Please go straight to the gym for a meet and greet with our Director. After some remarks from Mr. Dau you will then be dismissed to go to your student's classroom to hear more information from the teachers.

This Saturday, August 25th at 9:00 am GFA welcomes all "Guardians" to come participate in a School Beautification Day. This is a great opportunity to help out the community and also count some volunteer hours. Please remember to bring your rakes, shovels, wheelbarrows and gloves. Hope to see you there!

